latestIgtvVideos.title: REVIEW :- Huda Beauty Legit Lash Mascara
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Mascaras are my favourite beauty product, I am constantly amazed by how much difference a good mascara can make. Specially now that we’re all wearing masks and letting our eyes do the talking, a mascara is something you should definitely invest in. 
This is one mascara, that is going to go down in my top 5, for sure. Maybe even top 3. The more I use it, the more I like it. To be honest, the first time I used it I was quite disappointed to find out ( the hard way ) that this isn’t waterproof. But I got over that fact, as quickly as my mascara started to run once my eyes got a little ( read : a lot ) watery. 🤣 
This product does what it says :Curl, Length and Volume. 
For someone like me, whose lashes are as stubborn as a scorpion, the curl held up all day long; and I was the happiest girl in the world! 

This retails for ₹2,250 on @mynykaa & @sephora_india
